{"tid":1592260,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"24/9 21:14 (有片) 九龍灣站嘅便衣狗","createTime":"2019-09-24T13:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T14:17:03.000Z","uid":207038,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"76438695faa2bf106db566c44af98471ad6f24df","tid":1592260,"uid":207038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://streamable.com/ygyx3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fygyx3&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUoVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=5a7ef327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/ygyx3</a><br />\n有幾個人比閘內一隻狗同黨鐵職員扣查 開咗閘機 抽起咗一張（就我所見）特惠飛放落證物裝<br />\n我手機就黎冇電 影唔到相 我挨咗去個圍欄度 喺我諗住覆完野熄手機果陣 我發現我身後面多咗個大叔猛咁噉我部手機 99.99%係popo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想睇我有咩料料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我比咗句「望咩呀望？冇野呀話」佢就用個狗樣回咗句「冇咩呀」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我專登走上月台 攞部ipad影多一次就係想影埋你呢隻狗<br />\n可惜我果部係ipad2017好低清 加上擺去steamable好似又矇咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家記得影片取證果陣要小心身邊有冇呢啲人鬼鬼祟祟 唔好好似我咁掛住影野覆野 留意唔到後面多咗個大叔 好在 我果陣冇做啲咩 佢都做唔到啲咩"},{"pid":"eeca170a3df0af32aabc84aa7d27a547a7d76c2b","tid":1592260,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"7de097fc14524369720d822954de084926d85280","tid":1592260,"uid":207038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:50:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dba4e6ae2795e720109073472ec90e2e823b138a","tid":1592260,"uid":207038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:50:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pi